</ul>
<p><a name="Design_critiques" id="Design_critiques"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Usability&amp;action=edit&amp;section=34" title="Edit section: Design critiques">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Design critiques</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.baddesigns.com/index.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.baddesigns.com/index.shtml" rel="nofollow">Bad Human Factors Designs</a> — examples of bad design</li>
<li><a href="http://my.opera.com/usability/blog" class="external text" title="http://my.opera.com/usability/blog" rel="nofollow">User Centered</a> — critiques on design, usability discussion</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="References_2" id="References_2"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Usability&amp;action=edit&amp;section=35" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.interaction-design.org/encyclopedia/" class="external text" title="http://www.interaction-design.org/encyclopedia/" rel="nofollow">Interaction-Design.org</a> — an open-content encyclopedia about usability</li>
<li><a href="http://jthom.best.vwh.net/usability/" class="external text" title="http://jthom.best.vwh.net/usability/" rel="nofollow">jthom.best.vwh.net/usability</a> —Online guide to usability methods</li>
